body.value:
linear-gradient(
    to left,
    transparent var(--size-4-6),
    black var(--size-4-6)
  )

ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, "Segoe UI",
    Roboto, "Inter", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol",
    sans-serif

ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, "Cascadia Mono", "Roboto Mono",
    "DejaVu Sans Mono", "Liberation Mono", Menlo, Monaco, "Consolas",
    "Source Code Pro", monospace

.mod-rtl.value:
linear-gradient(
    to right,
    transparent var(--size-4-6),
    black var(--size-4-6)
  )

.workspace-leaf-resize-handle.value:
background-color 200ms ease-in-out,
    border-color 200ms ease-in-out,
    opacity 200ms ease-in-out

.checkbox-container.value:
box-shadow 0.15s ease-in-out,
    outline 0.15s ease-in-out,
    border 0.15s ease-in-out,
    opacity 0.15s ease-in-out

.checkbox-container:after.value:
transform 0.15s ease-in-out,
    width 0.1s ease-in-out,
    left 0.1s ease-in-out

.theme-dark .pdf-container.mod-themed .p.value:
drop-shadow(0px 0px 1px var(--color-base-60))
    drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4))
    drop-shadow(0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4))
